## ⚡ Power System

### 6. Battery & Power Management

| Item | Specifications | Quantity | Est. Price | Purchase Link |
|------|----------------|----------|------------|---------------|
| 7.4V Li-Po Battery | 2S 2200mAh 30C with XT60 connector | 1 | $15-18 | [Amazon](https://www.amazon.com/Zeee-Batteries-Helicopter-Airplane-Multi-Motor/dp/B07VRCL6YT) |
| LM2596 Buck Converter | DC-DC Step Down, adjustable 3-40V to 1.5-35V | 2 | $3 each ($6 total) | [Amazon](https://www.amazon.com/LAOMAO-Converter-1-23-30V-Adjustable-Regulator/dp/B089JYCKJL) |
| XT60 Connector | Male/Female pairs | 1 pair | $5 (10 pairs) | [Amazon](https://www.amazon.com/Amass-Female-Connector-Battery-10pairs/dp/B07VKKK73G) |
| Li-Po Battery Charger | B6 Balance Charger | 1 | $20-25 | [Amazon](https://www.amazon.com/Genuine-SKYRC-iMAX-Battery-Balance/dp/B0722NGPBS) |
| Power Switch | Heavy duty toggle switch 20A | 1 | $5 | [Amazon](https://www.amazon.com/Twidec-Toggle-Position-Waterproof-ASW-07D/dp/B07S2QJKTX) |

**Power Distribution:**
- Battery (7.4V) → Motors via L298N  
- Buck Converter 1 → 5V for Arduino  
- Buck Converter 2 → 5V for GPS & Bluetooth  

